title: At Journey's End: Bran Stark (Con Panel Audio)
description:
In the "At Journey's End" series, we look back on eight seasons of development for our favorite major characters. In this panel, we examine Bran's journey from the innocent boy who fell to the all-seeing Three-Eyed Raven.  Panelists: Val (Because Geek), Sanrixian, Phil TheIssuesGuy, and Sean of House Beard!
